    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to let this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a dream, and honestly feels like it just left the showroom floor. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the crazy dealership prices, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
